room_title: Escape room "Murder in the Old Manor House" by Escape Hunt in Cleveland
room_description: You are London detectives called to solve the murder of a man killed in his old manor house in Crownborough Village, England in 1914. Before arriving you receive a mysterious cipher message that seems to relate to the dead man. You have 60 minutes to solve the case and decipher the message before the crime scene is destroyed and the vital evidence is lost forever.
